00:35:09,066 --> 00:35:11,485
Mais cinco minutinhos, Jerry.

471
00:35:15,697 --> 00:35:16,740
Amanda, oi.

472
00:35:19,493 --> 00:35:21,954
Discurso de Gettysburg,
